You can use `@JsonInclude(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL)` annotation for the properties:

    class Foo {
    
        @JsonInclude(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL)
        int a;
    
        @JsonInclude(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL)
